{"tid":1890412,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"李英愛說中文聲援武漢！慰勞第一線醫護人員：中國一定能勝利","createTime":"2020-02-21T07:38:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T15:34:06.000Z","uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"230086ddbde8d3652bac1b712a6cb54487ac5248","tid":1890412,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T07:38:49.000Z","msg":"李英愛說中文聲援武漢！慰勞第一線醫護人員：中國一定能勝利<br />\n新冠肺炎（COVID-19）在南韓一夜之間再飆增52例，確診數已達156例。在各國努力抗疫期間，在中國享有高知名度的《大長今》女星李英愛也錄製影片為大陸打氣，特別以中文喊話，「武漢加油！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4715/d4715185.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4715%2Fd4715185.jpg&h=d5b81e47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲李英愛說中文聲援武漢。（圖／翻攝自中國駐韓國大使館）<br />\n<br />\n根據中國駐韓國大使館上午發布的影片中，特別找來因《大長今》在大陸享有盛名的南韓女星李英愛，她開口就用中文自介，「大家好，我是大長今李英愛。」並表示就像她在劇中帶領著大家戰勝瘟疫，「我相信中國一定能取得勝利」。<br />\n<br />\n李英愛也為第一線醫護人員加油，「在此向全力抗擊疫情的醫護工作者和全體中國人民，致以誠摯的慰問與支持。」並傳達韓國各界協助大陸不遺餘力，附上不少南韓國內應援中國的標語，甚至大樓點燈寫下「武漢加油」的字樣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4715/d4715186.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4715%2Fd4715186.jpg&h=5b3719a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲李英愛慰勞第一線醫護人員：中國一定能勝利。（圖／翻攝自中國駐韓國大使館）<br />\n<br />\n最後則與中國駐韓國大使刑海明一起並肩，單手握拳說出中文「守望相助，共克時艱。武漢加油！中國加油！」大力聲援武漢疫情。"},{"pid":"6a77c6d32042991b438bcf4fdec18b83cecc92c4","tid":1890412,"uid":289751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T07:40:17.000Z","msg":"韓國爆完未?"},{"pid":"5bb3de9532bfe0105383974f861ee2669237236f","tid":1890412,"uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6a77c6d32042991b438bcf4fdec18b83cecc92c4","tid":1890412,"uid":289751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T07:40:17.000Z","msg":"韓國爆完未?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T07:42:27.000Z","msg":"邪教有排爆"},{"pid":"e2a7efb41f11e13a5d73eafca108ea26cd5a47f9","tid":1890412,"uid":185238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T07:46:30.000Z","msg":"看黑警咳多轉未斷氣"},{"pid":"a24c5f2e98d624e1809579703c8d1456eceb758b","tid":1890412,"uid":236359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T07:55:13.000Z","msg":"慰勞"},{"pid":"d6a5c0d1852a405698803b2f595252ce0c001d58","tid":1890412,"uid":275370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T07:56:32.000Z","msg":"失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c5dcbed54bf3a4c7bd12ada6284d4557743f385","tid":1890412,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T07:56:41.000Z","msg":"搞咩鼻又歪嘴又歪"},{"pid":"92ba677999321bcfcc44b0139266d6943b6c2cc6","tid":1890412,"uid":154106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T10:01:03.000Z","msg":"睇孫飽好過睇老女人"},{"pid":"a2da89b804914c0c0b3c899f6d30f13b2dabf5df","tid":1890412,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T15:34:06.000Z","msg":"都唔明以前點解咁多人睇大長今，on撚99<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 冇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}